{"title":"The MADE Bike Show Returns August 23-25th, 2024","link":"https://theradavist.com/made-bike-show-returns-august-2024/","date":1701272406000,"content":"<p><em><a href=\"http://www.made.bike/\" target=\"_blank\">MADE</a>, the multi-day event for the handmade builder community, returns to Portland’s Zidell Yards August 23-25, 2024…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Made-edition-Moots-Routt-45-16.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>MADE (<a href=\"http://www.made.bike/\" target=\"_self\"><u>www.made.bike</u></a>), <a href=\"https://echoscomm.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ECHOS Communication</a>‘s multi-day industry and consumer event highlighting the global handmade community and the artisans and brands that support it, today announces its return to Portland’s Zidell Yards event venue and the opening of registration for exhibitors. In 2023, its inaugural year, MADE became the world’s largest custom bike show, bringing over 200 builders and brands together and attracting over 5000 attendees throughout the 3-day event.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Tomii-Cycles-Steel-Road-Bike-27.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Oscars-Simple-Bicycle-Co-27.522-Dirt-Jumper-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Ahearne-and-Igleheard-Page-Street-Tourer-15.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Scarab-Cycles-Darien-Hardtail-19.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>In 2024, MADE will return to Zidell Yards with a larger floor plan and venue footprint to accommodate additional exhibitors and attendees, as well as offering improved amenities. Exclusive industry and media hours will allow ample time to create dynamic content and connect builders and industry leaders. MADE will open to the public at 12 noon on Friday, August 23rd through Sunday, August 25th, 2024, with evening events spotlighting local cycling brands and culture.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Watts-Aero-Road-Bike-25.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Liberation-Fab-Yall-Road-23.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Significant-Other-Fixed-Gear-29.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Schon-Studio-Mini-Velo-17.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>MADE will offer new builders discounted booth space to ensure the entire handmade community has the opportunity to participate. With the Portland Waterfront as a backdrop, Zidell Yards is a perfect venue to showcase the unique bikes and components that will be on display. The 2024 show will see more food/coffee and beer vendors, along with multiple lounges, both indoor and outdoor, to provide attendees with additional options. A full show schedule and dates for ticket sales will be provided in Spring 2024.</p>\n<p>Registration for waitlisted brands and new exhibitors will begin at 8 AM PST on December 4th.</p>\n<p>MADE.bike</p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist will be back to bring you the most comprehensive coverage of MADE anywhere on the ‘net!</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Check out our collection of coverage in our Archives below!</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/made-bike-show-returns-august-2024/\">The MADE Bike Show Returns August 23-25th, 2024</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"6a51a17544e69d91a073f9ee266ef9a53e8ccdb94d2d67b924c20a7ca289bcf5","category":"Cycling"}